1
00:00:01,240 --> 00:00:02,800
(DOCTOR WHO THEME)

2
00:00:08,360 --> 00:00:10,120
(TELEPHONE RINGING)

3
00:00:23,480 --> 00:00:24,680
NIXON: Hello?

4
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:29,000
Hello, this is the President.

5
00:00:31,520 --> 00:00:34,720
Hello, this is the President
of the United States.

6
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:36,920
Who is this?

7
00:00:37,040 --> 00:00:38,320
(STATIC)

8
00:00:44,160 --> 00:00:46,840
-Is it you again?
-GIRL: Look behind you.

9
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:50,320
How did you get this number?

10
00:00:51,120 --> 00:00:52,520
This is my private line.

11
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:54,720
How did you get through?

12
00:00:55,760 --> 00:00:58,360
GIRL: They're everywhere. All the time.

13
00:00:58,680 --> 00:01:00,360
We see them every day.

14
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:03,200
But you have to look behind you.

15
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:05,320
NIXON: There is nothing behind me.

16
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:09,280
-How did you get this number?
-The spaceman told me.

17
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:14,160
-What spaceman?
-It doesn't matter.

18
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:17,640
I'm telling you about the monsters.

19
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:21,240
Please, you must look behind you.

20
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:26,240
Young lady, there are no monsters
in the Oval Office.

21
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:28,120
(PHONE DISCONNECTS)

